  "content": "<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\".AppleColorEmojiUI\">📜</font> 3. Professor POV &amp Actions – Dynamic Weekly Roles</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\".AppleColorEmojiUI\">📜</font> The professor’s in-class role is determined at the start of class, dictating available actions.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> Each week, the professor embodies a different POV/archetype that affects interactions.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> The chosen role dictates what the professor may do that session.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> Some roles allow powerful actions, while others limit control.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\".AppleColorEmojiUI\">📖</font> Possible Professor Roles &amp Powers</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><object><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; direction: ltr\">\n<tbody>\n<tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Role</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Inspired By</div>",
